{"tid":640334,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"MOMOLAND洗腦歌MV點擊破億！6月日本出道！","createTime":"2018-04-24T08:16:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T11:42:05.000Z","uid":182863,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"261147f1a2a64dc629990df081a0f70378d08d31","tid":640334,"uid":182863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T08:16:25.000Z","msg":"MOMOLAND的首個破億MV誕生！<br />\n<br />\n雖然被指抄襲和囤貨回購，但MOMOLAND年初發表的洗腦歌的確讓她們人氣急升，更是深深俘虜外國網友的心，而她們的《BBoom BBoom》MV也在23日正式突破1億瀏覽數！<br />\n<br />\nMOMOLAND於1月3日發行迷你專輯《GREAT!》，主打歌《BBoom BBoom》公開後成功晉身本年度最新洗腦歌，除了成功打入美國Billboard排行榜，這首歌至今仍在韓國音源榜佔據頭幾名，證明了大眾對歌曲的喜愛。<br />\n<br />\n《BBoom BBoom》MV也在23日突破1億瀏覽數，讚數也超過100萬，對於只是出道一年半的MOMOLAND是十分好的成績。<br />\n<br />\n另外，MOMOLAND即將於6月在日本出道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/161623_0b31e435e48b5a613d3d178fd1f030bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F161623_0b31e435e48b5a613d3d178fd1f030bc.png&h=acac65a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d059430ff3e9641a24799cc16192a277a3622481","tid":640334,"uid":182863,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T08:17:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Great!</span></span>"},{"pid":"54cc6b64ee8c2373647f84e97938e331d316a934","tid":640334,"uid":44638,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:44:30.000Z","msg":"佢地日本好似幾紅<br />\n<br />\n睇戶外showcase都幾多人<br />\n<br />\n不過一億真係唔簡單<br />\n<br />\n好多一線團都未有"},{"pid":"0870d2c0c1021ea436f4f0b630bf9f30b81820cd","tid":640334,"uid":27416,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54cc6b64ee8c2373647f84e97938e331d316a934","tid":640334,"uid":44638,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:44:30.000Z","msg":"佢地日本好似幾紅<br />\n<br />\n睇戶外showcase都幾多人<br />\n<br />\n不過一億真係唔簡單<br />\n<br />\n好多一線團都未有"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:57:38.000Z","msg":"除左bts twice bp 最快一億<im